locality: Manica e Sofala: Manica, Mavita (Posto antigo), Serra Mocuta.
Grassland with Hymenocardia acida and Annona senegalensis. 1 km from Ekouyi-Mboma. Dry recently burned grasslands.
Léfini Animal Reserve: Grassland on lower slopes of Léfini ravine. Savanna-grassland, scattered shrubs, mostly Hymenocardia acida, sparse Annona senegalensis.
Plants of Selous Game Reserve, Tanzania. t6-c.8 km S of Ruaha Camp.
